    "name": "Necrocat Demo",
    "steam_appid": 3245430,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮助击败可怕的死灵猫，将游戏添加到您的愿望单中！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245430/extras/41c79dc94f36fb5da1bedc8fd430b54f.poster.avif?t=1747147070\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245430/extras/41c79dc94f36fb5da1bedc8fd430b54f.webm?t=1747147070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245430/extras/41c79dc94f36fb5da1bedc8fd430b54f.mp4?t=1747147070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Necrocat 是一款简单但具有深度策略的卡牌掘矿游戏。蹭身Twilight，在战场中移动，尽力對抗惊怕的Necrocat军队，并收集物品以帮助你进步泼涟术士的路线!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245430/extras/82e48f2a0622e963d4966ae562a6902c.avif?t=1747147070\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245430/extras_big/82e48f2a0622e963d4966ae562a6902c.avif?t=1747147070 width=800 height=208 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >击败Necrocat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你的前进，你会遇到各种卡牌，这些卡牌代表着Twilight收集和使用的物品，用于对抗惊怕的Necrocat召唤的尸魂大军。你的目标很清楚：毁灭所有怪物，并揭开泼涟术士惊惊称号之后的黑暗真相。为了战胜他，你必须收集Necrocat的所有护身天使，这些护身天使内含他暗黑灵魂的碎片。在每次胜利后，收集的护身天使将带来更强大的能力，使Twilight每次回到战场时都变得更加强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >变强大!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集你所有发现的护身天使，并升级它们，以获得更强大的力量！或许你无法被劳而与所有挑战相抱，但随着你收集更多的护身天使，并使用它们对抗泼涟术士的军队，Necrocat将变得更脆弱，你也将进步接近与他的激战!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245430/extras/701b25bfa8db0de75589799f7e723246.poster.avif?t=1747147070\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245430/extras/701b25bfa8db0de75589799f7e723246.webm?t=1747147070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245430/extras/701b25bfa8db0de75589799f7e723246.mp4?t=1747147070\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要机制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在各种大小的卡牌格子中，你可以乐趣游玩，只需选择你想移动的方向，以收集物品或与怪物战斗。随着怪物被毁灭，更强大的怪物将出现，战胜它们将获得更丰厚的奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使用策略游玩!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个区域或地图都拥有不同数量的敌人和物品，且战场大小和形状各不相同。有些物品在更小的或更大的场地上更有效，而每种地图都需要独特的策略，如果你想超越限制，真正击败Necrocat。</p>",
